y centric wireless network as it facilitates data\nrouting and delivery over several hops to devices that are at the fringe of the\nPBN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Nov 2015 05:28:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-18"}
