ibria and abundances determined from the\natomic CI (NLTE) and molecular CH species supports the parameters we derived\nwith SME by fitting the observed spectra including the hydrogen lines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Nov 2015 12:17:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
